description:
**Artist's Description:** 
 
resently, i fall in love with an adorable magical girl's anime call "Precure A la mode" ,   
it's the 12 generation of precure in 2017, and themed as "Sweets" 
 
they may not good at the story line here i must said.. =_=...   
but the desgin and cuteness is somethgin i never forget, that's why i spend most of the time tring to combine my pony art with it. 
 
the second time when i recheck Derpibooru, i wondering if there's any art have the precure theme, but it came out a few number  
it's ... kind of disturbing when you think of it... like if i want to starting the style, will i get enough followers? i thought thought and i thought. 
 
i must be honest... i don't know what you guys like or favor... i 'm not smart.. so i only do artworks that came from my own inspiration. but ...if this some kind of style, i think it's worth to try...   
that's how this Gelato Rainbodash was born, and it's going to display in Canterlot Royal Ballet Academy series gallery. (set as the new skin of Mane6 ballet outfit) 
 
Cure gelato is the precure of icey sweets, like ice cream and gelato those thing, and the animal it repersent are lion. the icecream dress i rdesgin it, make it more detailful, and Rainbow's mane become some puffy lion mane type, with the sweet little pointy teeth showing in her month. may this little angel cool down your heart under the hot bruning summer sun 
 
it's been a long time, i don't know if i still got fans in derpibooru, but if it does... i'm very appreciate that,  your support, feedback and comment are my strength to continue this . and i hope you enjoy today's feature.  
 
I'll see you next time 
 
  
Sean.M
